This is a walk in clinic being held at Capital Mall, 625 Black Lake Blvd SW, Olympia WA, 98502 daily from 12pm until mall closing. We will be located inside the mall, closest to the Sephora end of the mall and next to the Buckle store. • All minors 12 to 17 years old must receive parent or guardian consent to receive a COVID-19 vaccine. If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.
